{"tid":514191,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇做teller既人入黎傾下計","createTime":"2017-12-30T10:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T10:08:28.000Z","uid":58269,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"714973e741e10ed4ab1e57c359187546097c1fed","tid":514191,"uid":58269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:03:28.000Z","msg":"今日遇到個八婆真係勁閪 <br />\n比左兩本簿我打 一本公司一本私人<br />\n<br />\n我：你本簿凍結左喎(公司）<br />\n八婆：我之前先入過錢咋喎<br />\n我：本簿係咪你自己架<br />\n八婆：打簿咋喎 唔得架咩（啲語氣勁閪）<br />\n我：我照打啦咁<br />\n八婆：我之前入錢都當郁左個戶口架啦？（拎住私人本簿問）<br />\n我點頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢再問：咁你又話凍結左！<br />\n我：係公司嗰本凍結 私人嗰本冇<br />\n佢：咁我之前咪入左囉！！！<br />\n我：哦 咁你話入左咪得囉<br />\n佢：你可唔可以唔好咁既態度呢？廢話<br />\n<br />\n屌！！真係痴線 自己態度閪又要期望人地態度好<br />\n你點對人咪點對你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  嬲撚到我"},{"pid":"907c8049d84f1a1facddc4115634452c89cf1ca0","tid":514191,"uid":68626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:08:14.000Z","msg":"讀緊u做個陣<br />\n試過比廢老話我偷佢錢想報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f580636ae03d1f65eb4312e8411b6001a0d2995","tid":514191,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:16:20.000Z","msg":"呢啲冇禮貌撚唔死都冇用<br />\n<br />\n利申：story teller"},{"pid":"5a40171117555e93a0aec3ac5131ffd5f1710660","tid":514191,"uid":102904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:18:45.000Z","msg":"如果無啦啦有客想識你問你攞電話俾唔俾？"},{"pid":"02e88f271eec0f809528488dd849c3de70776b2c","tid":514191,"uid":58269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀緊u做個陣<br />\n試過比廢老話我偷佢錢想報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好憎啲廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日先比一個鬧完黎<img src=