uote><blockquote><blockquote>如果無啦啦有客想識你問你攞電話俾唔俾？</blockquote><br />\n咁突然<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時見到又啱feel真係想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實 teller難唔難搵對象？</blockquote><br />\n比個電話佢搵你好似好啲<br />\n我覺得難</blockquote><br />\n用咩籍口俾電話好？因為通常都俾身份證佢check,佢喺電腦一㩒就知我電話號碼<br />\n<br />\n點解難啊？我見teller男女都有喎，朝夕相對應該唔難識"},{"pid":"566cd3c5a9ef8e7d73039eed8fe7467b7fcee20a","tid":514191,"uid":58269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無銀行請pt teller?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀緊u 想grad左入銀行做</blockquote><br />\n我見Hsbc有請 但銀行真係唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185045766ffc476b10a1bbad13d4cf551a07d928","tid":514191,"uid":58269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果無啦啦有客想識你問你攞電話俾唔俾？</blockquote><br />\n咁突然<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時見到又啱feel真係想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實 teller難唔難搵對象？</blockquote><br />\n比個電話佢搵你好似好啲<br />\n我覺得難</blockquote><br />\n用咩籍口俾電話好？因為通常都俾身份證佢check,佢喺電腦一㩒就知我電話號碼<br />\n<br />\n點解難啊？我見teller男女都有喎，朝夕相對應該唔難識</blockquote><br />\n係check到 但唔會私自搵客架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你一係直接寫張紙仔比佢<br />\n難唔難睇做邊區"},{"pid":"8d0082e5cb872b26b3708df207b5c367e2d6a2ef","tid":514191,"uid":58269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:13:12.000Z","msg":"點解負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係想發洩下咋<br />\n係咪我做錯啲咩"},{"pid":"6f86d20ea4e31d412539f88dd6a54a91bc329a2b","tid":514191,"uid":38957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:19:14.000Z","msg":"香港人特別係啲廢老係咁西，加油巴打"},{"pid":"d821c6ebb5cf96b0189ec33f63871e25f6df522f","tid":514191,"uid":54776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d0082e5cb872b26b3708df207b5c367e2d6a2ef","tid":514191,"uid":58269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:13:12.000Z","msg":"點解負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係想發洩下咋<br />\n係咪我做錯啲咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:19:44.000Z","msg":"表示認感認同<br />\n做緊part time call center"},{"pid":"c3692c4316ab6dd0d14a22fa860574bafd38ddff","tid":514191,"uid":102904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係想發洩下咋<br />\n係咪我做錯啲咩</blockquote><br />\n我明呀<br />\n有時排係啲西客後面都覺得個teller好慘<br />\n以為有小小錢就好巴閉<br />\n自己蠢又以為自己好醒<br />\n明明人地同你講清講楚但自己get錯，之後就話人地做錯"},{"pid":"a9691844000ccf8201ac43467111e36abf74ed74","tid":514191,"uid":102904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果無啦啦有客想識你問你攞電話俾唔俾？</blockquote><br />\n咁突然<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時見到又啱feel真係想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實 teller難唔難搵對象？</blockquote><br />\n比個電話佢搵你好似好啲<br />\n我覺得難</blockquote><br />\n用咩籍口俾電話好？因為通常都俾身份證佢check,佢喺電腦一㩒就知我電話號碼<br />\n<br />\n點解難啊？我見teller男女都有喎，朝夕相對應該唔難識</blockquote><br />\n係check到 但唔會私自搵客架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你一係直接寫張紙仔比佢<br />\n難唔難睇做邊區</blockquote><br />\n無啦啦俾張紙仔teller我驚佢以為我想打劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲區男女teller 好唔平衡？"},{"pid":"58c71d22c